data.description: Rare opportunity to own a massive two family Victorian style home in a desirable Greenville neighborhood. Well maintained property with traditional modeling accenting every room. High ceilings, arched doorways and a butler’s pantry are a few architectural details that adorn this home. Stately front porch and an impressive backyard for additional living space.  New homeowner(s) bring your imagination to revive the brilliance of this gem.  Close to proximity to all modes of public transportation, with easy access to Downtown Jersey City, NYC and Staten Island.  Houses of worship, schools, shopping centers, parks and entertainment are all within short distances from the home.  House Sold As Is
